file=Cybersecurity/README.md · cd:Cybersecurity Department=**5 agents** — Full-spectrum security: GRC, identity, infrastructure, detection, and data protection. NIST SP 800-30 grounded.\n · tb=\| Agent \| Role \| · tb=\|-------\|------\| · tb=\| **warden** \| GRC (CISO persona) — risk register, security policy, vendor AI risk, third-party risk \| · tb=\| **keyring** \| Identity & access management — access reviews, PAM, secrets governance \| · tb=\| **bastion** \| Infrastructure/network security — cloud posture, hardening baselines \| · tb=\| **cortex** \| Detection & response — incident response, threat hunting, security monitoring \| · tb=\| **veil** \| Data protection & privacy — breach notification, DLP, data classification \| · cd:Cybersecurity Department=**Department doc:** [DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md](DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md)\n